Create ou edit /root/.asoundrc file, edit the hw:x,y text accordingly.

pcm.!default {
         type asym
         playback.pcm {
                 type plug
                 slave.pcm "hw:0,0"
         }
         capture.pcm {
                 type plug
                 slave.pcm "hw:1,0"
         } 
 }

Reboot ?